beer.beer_description: This gin basil smash pays tribute to the glorious cocktail it was inspired by. The flavours will toy with you with every sip. Hints of fragrant spice from the juniper and a fresh playfulness from the basil, with a touch of tart sweetness from the lime will wash over you as you indulge your sensees. The gin that was added late in the fermentation process dances on the finish of the palette, making this delightful beer the perfect companion in a gin boilermaker.
